---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Sri Lankan Coconut Sauce with Garlic Veggies & Sesame Rice
description: We've turbo-charged schnitzel night with some unexpected, yet delightful additions! You'll find a featuring of a too good to be true creamy coconut sauce infused with Sri Lankan-style spices, some fluffy rice and a helping of garlic veggies. With immaculate
combos like these, it's nothing but happy days ahead!
